Carnifex Maximus Vardorvis was an individual of unknown race, that presumably lived during the Third Age. He was personally hunting Yonrith Lovakengj, an opposing army leader.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Carnifex Maximus is Latin and translates to 'greatest executioner' or 'greatest butcher'.
    • Vardorvis was presumably a Zarosian as the title is similar to those that Zamorak and Azzanadra had in RuneScape, when they both were in the service of Zaros.
rawContent:
Carnifex Maximus '''Vardorvis''' was an individual of unknown race, that presumably lived during the [[Third Age]]. He was personally hunting [[Yonrith Lovakengj]], an opposing army leader. 

==Trivia==
* Carnifex Maximus is Latin and translates to 'greatest executioner' or 'greatest butcher'.
** Vardorvis was presumably a [[Zaros]]ian as the title is similar to those that [[Zamorak]] and [[Azzanadra]] had in ''RuneScape'', when they both were in the service of Zaros.
